about_me.content: In September 2022, I packed up my bags and flew 2,500 miles from Boston, MA to Seattle, WA to embark on a new adventure to discover my interest in computer science and software engineering. Today, I'm learning to master Python, HTML/CSS, and Javascript.

Prior to joining Ada, I worked as an Senior Analyst at Hercules Capital, conducting financial due diligence for start-ups within the tech industry. Over my 1.5-year tenure, I led and participated in qualitative and quantitive analysis of ten companies, totaling to over $500M in commitments invested. 
 Come along for the journey!
